  "detailed_description": "在《太古洪荒》中，玩家将从上帝视角指引角色修炼生产并建立自己的宗门。没有繁琐的操作，无论是生产、战斗抑或是秘境探险，游戏都做到足够的放置。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/14909803b4e4b9f33a03a30d879a08af.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>地图随机产生，仔细规划资源进行占领。<br></li><li>生产资源时也要考虑灵气的流动。<br></li><li>灵气匮乏或者富集都会导致秘境的产生。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/41308f30af2b639013a19043816b2db8.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>一切皆是任务。<br></li><li>没有过多干预，掌门只可指定任务的内容和奖励。<br></li><li>无需指派，弟子根据自身能力和性格自行选择喜欢的任务。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/34b9a7b563e12ddb65601ac860090035.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>自走棋式的战斗。<br></li><li>增援机制带来大量的变数。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >秘境</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/3f53922812f33dce58b5de03844d2dff.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>掌门可以派遣指定弟子开始探险。<br></li><li>弟子属性为秘境探险路线带来不确定性。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功法</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/28e0702815a67420ee186b294f007e01.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>完全随机的功法系统。<br></li><li>刀、剑、枪、棍、拳、法术、体术、医术、阵法、符篆、心法等多种各具特色的功法类型。</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "在《太古洪荒》中，玩家将从上帝视角指引角色修炼生产并建立自己的宗门。没有繁琐的操作，无论是生产、战斗抑或是秘境探险，游戏都做到足够的放置。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/14909803b4e4b9f33a03a30d879a08af.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>地图随机产生，仔细规划资源进行占领。<br></li><li>生产资源时也要考虑灵气的流动。<br></li><li>灵气匮乏或者富集都会导致秘境的产生。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/41308f30af2b639013a19043816b2db8.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>一切皆是任务。<br></li><li>没有过多干预，掌门只可指定任务的内容和奖励。<br></li><li>无需指派，弟子根据自身能力和性格自行选择喜欢的任务。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/34b9a7b563e12ddb65601ac860090035.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>自走棋式的战斗。<br></li><li>增援机制带来大量的变数。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >秘境</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/3f53922812f33dce58b5de03844d2dff.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>掌门可以派遣指定弟子开始探险。<br></li><li>弟子属性为秘境探险路线带来不确定性。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功法</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018300/extras/28e0702815a67420ee186b294f007e01.avif?t=1729691887\" width=500 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>完全随机的功法系统。<br></li><li>刀、剑、枪、棍、拳、法术、体术、医术、阵法、符篆、心法等多种各具特色的功法类型。</li></ul>",
